-- Halliburton May Bid 3.1 Billion Pounds for John Wood, Mail Says
-- B y   C h r i s   P e t e r s o n
-- 2010-11-16T07:31:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-16/halliburton-may-bid-4-97-billion-for-oil-company-john-wood-mail-reports.html
Halliburton Co. may bid 3.1 billion
($4.97 billion), or 595 pence a share, for U.K.-based oil and
gas services contractor John Wood Group Plc, the Daily Mail
reported, without saying where it obtained the information.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
